# samples/ — Source and License Per File

This directory ships demo data + a query template that the RelyLoop tutorial
([`docs/08_guides/tutorial-first-study.md`](../docs/08_guides/tutorial-first-study.md))
seeds into the local Elasticsearch container and uses for a 10-trial study.
Each artifact's source and license are documented below.

| File | Source | License |
|---|---|---|
| `products.json` | Subset of the [Amazon Shopping Queries Dataset (ESCI)](https://github.com/amazon-science/esci-data) | CC-BY-4.0 (Amazon) |
| `queries.csv` | Subset of the same dataset | CC-BY-4.0 (Amazon) |
| `templates/product_search.j2` | Original RelyLoop authorship | MIT (RelyLoop) |
| `LICENSE` (this file) | Original RelyLoop authorship | MIT (RelyLoop) |

